{"tid":178100,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩睇完Fate stay night ubw 好唔開心 求安慰","createTime":"2017-03-29T10:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T07:43:13.000Z","uid":78016,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f35dd30b4a8b320a1602a01b0b92a8f3006e03ff","tid":178100,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T10:03:27.000Z","msg":"唔開心原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1. 土朗同凛無係動畫做愛補充魔力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. Saber 最後消失左<br />\n3. 土朗係後記同凛一齊住都唔親密 莫講話要補充魔力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4. 龍汁=MP,做愛=補充魔力 呢D設定無曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前睇第一套Fate 又係咁<br />\n明明土朗要同Saber 做愛補充魔力<br />\n動畫on99又skip左<br />\n宜家睇返UBW 又係咁 又Skip左土朗同凛做愛補充魔力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過UBW凛真係好正 要永遠陪伴土朗令土朗開心<br />\n又睇完一套動畫真係好Sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然作者俾左個Happy ending 我地<br />\n唉 求安慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18420030aa767695945711c8a39d7c161a0cb663","tid":178100,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T10:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafbcec4221e9345fe1b1eacee7d85e0e6680d3d","tid":178100,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T10:08:54.000Z","msg":"你睇咩版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla